			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Go to act 1b. &#xD;&#xA;Go the security office and accept or refuse Vlaakith's mission. &#xD;&#xA;284; 2; 305&#xD;&#xA;SetGlobalOsirisFlag CRE_ChainOfCommand_State_PlanecasterActive &#xD;&#xA;Insert the Artefact into the planecaster object&#xD;&#xA;Once in the astral prison, follow the wisp to its final destination and talk to it." />
